summary: Small application used to sort mods through your Mod Organizer profiles.
descriptionHtml:
[center][color=#6aa84f][size=6]Mod Organizer Sorter

[/size][/color][size=3]This small application can help you manage mod installation order when using [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/1334/?]Mod Organizer[/url].[/size][/center][left]
To anyone learning to program, check out this app's GitHub here: [url=https://github.com/Alekskill124/mo_sorter]GitHub[/url], even though this was done pretty quickly [/left]
author: Alekskill124
